---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Techniques
description: How to do the things that make cooking work -- knife skills, heat, fermentation, doughs, and the rest.
permalink: /techniques/
section: techniques
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<div aria-hidden="true" style="display:none">
  <span data-pagefind-meta="section">Techniques</span>
  <span data-pagefind-filter="section">techniques</span>
</div>

<header class="recipe-hero container">
  <span class="recipe-hero__eyebrow">Index</span>
  <h1 class="recipe-hero__title">Techniques</h1>
  <p class="recipe-hero__dek">The mechanics behind the recipes. Read one before you cook one.</p>
</header>

<section class="container" style="margin-top: var(--space-8);">
  {% set techniquesList = collections.techniques | reverse %}
  {% if techniquesList.length > 0 %}
  <div class="recipe-grid">
    {% for recipe in techniquesList %}
      {% set recipe = recipe %}
      {% include "partials/recipe-card.njk" %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% else %}
  <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--text-md); color: var(--color-ink-faint);">No technique guides published yet. <a href="/submit/technique/" style="color: var(--color-accent);">Pitch one</a>.</p>
  {% endif %}
</section>
